Title: Fix possible error using "Events of application" link
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Component: multisite
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Edition: cre
State: unknown
Version: 1.6.0p30
Date: 1658299416

If the burger menu entry "Events of application" was used and the application
name contained slashes, the link led to an error like "Unhandled exception:
400: Filter: invalid escape sequence: \T".
